  "text": "Greedy based algorithms [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] use different approach to construct redescriptions. The algorithm first constructs initial redescriptions that are obtained by pairwise attribute exploration. Then, candidate redescription is iteratively extended to increase accuracy. The worst time complexity of this algorithms is no less than O(|V 1 | · |V 2 | · |E|).",
